### Welcome to FlexGP!
FlexGP is a Evolutionary Computation framework aimed at data modeling and knowledge discovery. In this website we provide a quick tutorial to get started and model your data.



```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```
